h3. Problem definition
Currently, when *Cloning* and Issue, it is not possible to hide/remove the *Clone Attachments* checkbox.
  !JirraIssueClone.png|thumbnail! 

h3. Workaround
Add the following css script in your Jira Announcement Banner (by following the steps on   [Configuring an announcement banner KB|https://confluence.atlassian.com/adminjiraserver/configuring-an-announcement-banner-938846985.html]), *Clone Attachments* checkbox will disappear:
{code:xml}
<script type="text/javascript">
// if an XHR request completed
AJS.$( document ).ajaxComplete(function( event,request, settings ) {
  // if it was a click on the Clone button
  if(settings.url.indexOf('CloneIssueDetails') >= 0){
    // hide the attachments checkbox
      AJS.$('form#clone-issue.aui > div.form-body > fieldset > fieldset.group > div.checkbox').each(function(){
        if($( this ).html().indexOf("clone-issue-clone-attachments") >= 0){
          $( this ).hide();
        }
      });
  }
});
</script>
{code}
